node.text:
I am stoked to be joining the @ouraring team! 
I push myself as hard as I can everyday and for years I only relied on my morning heart rate and how I felt when I woke up. Where is now, I’m able to be super analytical and learn things about myself I didn’t even know. It helps me figure out how hard I should push or how much recovery I need. It has been a great tool for helping me achieve my best! 💯 #ouraring 
Pics: @zaknoyle

node.text:
In the grand scheme of things I’m just a speck of dust. However I have found motivation drive & purpose through setting goals to chase after. Doing whatever it takes to be “another day better” is the current mantra. 
Riding with @pinarello_us has been one of the ways I am able to elevate myself to the next level. #aSpeckofDust Full film is now on YouTube at Pinarello’s Channel 🚴
